# Google Apps Script Web App URL (REQUIRED)
# Steps:
# 1. Open your Google Sheet → Extensions → Apps Script
# 2. Paste Code.gs, set DRIVE_FOLDER_ID
# 3. Deploy → New Deployment → Web App → Anyone → Deploy
# 4. Copy the Web App URL and paste it below
VITE_GOOGLE_SCRIPT_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_DEPLOYMENT_ID/exec
